item.title: Bonus edition: A double dose of holidays from hell
item.description:
We read the papers so you don’t have to, now every Monday and Friday. Today: Brace yourselves for the 'Holidays from Hell' mini pod! Miranda tells Jason the tale of a luxury cruise ship marooned in Belfast Lough. Meanwhile, Jan and Jonn dive into holiday horror stories in The Fence (Britain’s only magazine). Miranda Sawyer is joined by fan favourite panellists Jonn Elledge, Jan Ravens and Jason Hazeley.
Come and see us LIVE at the Cheerful Earful podcast festival on 12 Oct... Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/PMO4839794651
